CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 5, 1955, pg. 13 reads: "Glamour - Mrs. Maxwell Johnson (seated left) of Aliquippa, and Mrs. William C. Session of Clairton, are pictured here with their aides at their smart luncheon-bridge party held last week in Horizon Room of the Greater Pittsburgh Airport. Left to right: Mrs. Thomas Stokes and Mrs. George Little stand behind the young matrons. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four women, front row; Mrs. Maxwell Johnson and Mrs. William C. Session, wearing polka dot dress; back row; Mrs. Thomas Stokes and Mrs. George Little, posed in the Horizon Room of the Greater Pittsburgh Airport, another version
